dct_title_s: Guide map of Mussoorie and Landour
dct_description_sm: Survey of India. "Refer to this map as: Eight inch Mussoorie and Landour guide map, third edition." Relief shown by 100 feet contour interval, spot heights, and rock drawings. Surveyed 1920. 1st ed 1922, 2nd ed. 1929. With a distances table. Inset maps: designated A-D for map continuation.
